# üåä BlueMotion Surf | Premium Surfing Landing Page

A sleek, responsive, and high-performance landing page designed for an ocean lifestyle brand. This project demonstrates modern front-end techniques including **CSS Grid**, **Glassmorphism UI**, **Vanilla JavaScript animations**, and a custom-built **Lightbox gallery**.

